  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    Errors.ErrorMatcher<R>
    A visitor interface that can be used in producing functions on Errors objects.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Data<META,DATA>
    A Data object contains a data object and a metadata object of the given types.
    DummyErrorWriterImpl  
    Errors
    A container for any one of the various error types.
    ErrorWriterImpl
    Holds a writer function for producing a JsonObject from an Errors.
    Filters
    Functions for extracting filters from metadata.
    ForecastApp
    An application that takes a label for a forecast process as a command line argument and runs that process from STDIN to STDOUT.
    ForecastFunctions
    Functions that do forecasts, and various methods used in building them.
    ForecastProcess
    A ForecastProcess contains a function for turning an input JsonObject into a result JsonObject.
    ForecastProcesses
    A ForecastProcesses contains a mapping from String to ForecastProcess and provides a method for running a given ForecastProcess -- taking its json input from a given InputStream and writing the result JsonObject into the given OutputStream.
    Formats
    Contains approved readers and writers for types of JSON input and output.
    Formats.Reader<META,DATA>
    A Reader defines a way of turning a JsonObject into data and metadata objects of the given types.
    Formats.Writer<META,RESULT>
    A Writer defines a way of producing a JsonObject from an object of a given forecast result data type and from additional information from an object of a given metadata type.
    JsonUtils
    Various tools for dealing with JSON input and output.
    LeastSquaresApp
    An application that runs the least squares process from STDIN to STDOUT.
    Time
    Miscellaneous time-related utilities.
    TimedValue<V>
    A value associated with a moment in time.
    Utils
    Miscellaneous utilities.
    Zab
    Metadata for the 'zab' format.
